A clean and responsive Movie Finder application built with Vanilla JavaScript, HTML, and CSS.
Users can search for movies, explore genres, and view detailed information using a public movie API (TMDb / OMDb).

ğŸš€ Features

Live Movie Search (with dropdown suggestions)

Search Results Page with pagination

Movie Details Page including cast, crew, runtime, ratings, and genres

Genre Page to filter movies by categories

Loading, Error, and Empty States for better UX

Fully Responsive (mobile, tablet, desktop)

index.html # Home page
search.html # Search results page
movie.html # Movie details page
genre.html # Genre listing page

âš¡ Usage

Open index.html in your browser.

Start typing in the search bar to see movie suggestions.

Press Enter to view full search results.

Click any movie to view detailed information.

Navigate through genres to discover more movies.

